# Specs Module

## Overview

Spec pyramid supports Goals → Architecture → Designs → Plans → Tests → Reviews → Reports with no APIs category

## Goals

- **G1** — Spec pyramid supports Goals → Architecture → Designs → Plans → Tests → Reviews → Reports with no APIs category
- **G2** — Specs Workspace with Bidirectional Traceability
- **G3** — Seven spec categories render with structured per-category editors
- **G4** — RelationsPanel shows upstream parents and downstream children
- **G5** — AutoLinkContent parses typed IDs into clickable hyperlinks
- **G6** — Drift Check button compares code against specs on demand
- *...and 5 more*

## Key Architecture Decisions

- **A1** — Goals Hierarchy Architecture

## Key Designs

- **D1** — Category Renderer Polymorphism
- **D2** — RelationsPanel & AutoLinkContent
- **D3** — GateBanner (Specs View)
- **D4** — GoalsTable Tree View Component
- **D5** — GoalDetailModal Component
- **D6** — Spec Tag Display & Sidebar Filtering
- **D7** — Backend Flat Mode Project Resolution
- *...and 2 more*

## Module Dependencies

Depends on: [agent-config](agent-config/module.ad), [chat](chat/module.ad), [relay](relay/module.ad), [ui-system](ui-system/module.ad)

